{"data":[{"date":"22:09 03/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u TBN trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/tan-hlv-bayern-munich-da-deu-tbn-trong-ngay-ra-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern Munich m\u1edbi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac nhanh ch\u00f3ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ecf nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 t\u00e2n binh Serge Gnabry.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Bayern Munich m\u1eddi l\u1ea1i Jupp Heynckes \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n CLB theo d\u1ea1ng \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d sau khi sa th\u1ea3i Carlo Ancelotti v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c H\u00f9m X\u00e1m x\u1ee9 Bavaria ph\u1ea3i \u0111i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Niko Kovac, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Croatia m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua hai n\u0103m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Eintracht Frankfurt, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n khi ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bayern Munich trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/tan-hlv-bayern-munich-da-deu-tbn-trong-ngay-ra-mat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i (Kovac t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o H\u00f9m X\u00e1m kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian 2001-2003) v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft. CLB \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn lao v\u00e0o t\u00f4i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Anh em t\u00f4i (tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Robert Kovac) \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Croatia c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ecf k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u1edf Allianz Arena khi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Robert Lewandowski, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfm ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y ra \u0111i v\u00ec h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 Arjen Robben v\u00e0 Franck Ribery c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u201csao x\u1eb9t\u201d Renato Sanches, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ante Rebic, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf Frankfurt v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y, H\u00f9m X\u00e1m ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Serge Gnabry, c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Werder Bremen, nh\u01b0ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c cho Hoffenheim m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua v\u00e0 gi\u1edd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Allianz Arena v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 22.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tan binh Serge Gnabry cua Bayern Munich\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Serge Gnabry c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Gnabry.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Serge Gnabry c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cLouis van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh phong c\u00e1ch cho Bayern Munich v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch B v\u00e0 C t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 80% tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.\u201d - Kovac tranh th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u TBN sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-ngay-la-roja-mac-ket-giua-hai-the-he-421-190135.html\">TBN b\u1eadt b\u00e3i World Cup 2018: Ng\u00e0y La Roja m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t gi\u1eefa hai th\u1ebf h\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tbn-vs-nga-toi-dep-khong-den-voi-nguoi-cho-doi-421-190136.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u ra \u0111i: T\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i n\u00f3</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3966","checkdouble":"190306"},{"date":"20:24 03/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 3/7: Real Madrid ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/4/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-37-real-madrid-phu-nhan-lien-he-voi-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 3/7.</h2><h2>Arsenal nh\u1eafm Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Independent kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. HLV Unai Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates khi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Mahrez s\u1eafp ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Sky Sports, Riyad Mahrez s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf Man City trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi &ldquo;b\u1ea7y c\u00e1o&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Algeria. V\u00e0 anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man xanh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Willian mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barcelona. Nh\u01b0ng The Blues s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Willian v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020. V\u00e0 Chelsea mong mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 80 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 37 Real ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 37 Real ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-37-Real-phu-nhan-mua-Neymar-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 3/7: Real ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar. K\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh TVE c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 310 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1edbi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Neymar. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi PSG v\u1ec1 Neymar trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<h2>PSG nh\u1eafm Bonucci</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Calciomercato, PSG \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci b\u00ean ph\u00eda Milan. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Gianluigi Buffon trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Bonucci.</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 2 t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Marca, Barcelona s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil l\u00e0 Clement Lenglet v\u00e0 Arthur trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. Lenglet s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n trong khi Arthur \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona. Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao Frenkie De Jong c\u1ee7a Ajax v\u00e0 Golovin c\u1ee7a Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-27-ngay-dau-nham-chuc-hlv-bayern-da-gieo-sau-cho-real-184-190203.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2/7: M\u1edbi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, HLV Bayern \u0111\u00e3 gieo s\u1ea7u cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-17-kroos-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-184-190106.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/7: Kroos b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3965","checkdouble":"190300"},{"date":"22:30 03/07","title":"V\u1eeba sang DC United, Rooney nh\u1eadn vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u2013 Wayne Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho ng\u00e0y 2/7 h\u00e0ng n\u0103m.\r\n</h2><h2>Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ng\u00e0y<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c G\u00e3 Shrek c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o DC United. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (2/7), anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y 3 m\u00f9a r\u01b0\u1ee1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia y\u00eau th\u00edch m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 r\u1ea5t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Man United &ndash; CLB n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady ngay khi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Old Trafford t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney trong mau ao DC\" title=\"Rooney trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o DC\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o DC United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Washington DC, Muriel Bowser \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y t\u00ean Rooney \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t cho ng\u00e0y 2/7. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 &ldquo;Wayne Rooney Day&rdquo;. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ng\u00e0y Rooney s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf bang Washington.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay 32 tu\u1ed5i, Rooney cho bi\u1ebft quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sang M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e0m ti\u1ebfu.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ngay trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u1edf h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7c h\u00e3y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n si\u00eang n\u0103ng, v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney duoc vinh danh boi thi truong bang Washington DC\" title=\"Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh b\u1edfi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng bang Washington DC\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/roon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh b\u1edfi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng bang Washington DC</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Washington l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn, \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c t\u1ed1t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Los Angeles v\u00e0 New York qu\u00e1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 London v\u1eady. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn London. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng gian ri\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh xa m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, v\u00e0 DC United cho t\u00f4i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi &ndash; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y CLB khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng SV\u0110 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay-421-190252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay-421-190252.html\">Rooney: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh v\u1edbi Colombia v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi-172-189906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi-172-189906.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Rooney x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3964","checkdouble":"190307"},{"date":"18:16 03/07","title":"Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/9/barca-cong-bo-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet c\u1ee7a Sevilla.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Arthur v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3 v\u1eeba qua, Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. 30 tri\u1ec7u euro s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, 10 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 2 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 2 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-cong-bo-2-tan-binh-vao-dau-tuan-toi-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Arthur v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Arthur. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u song Barca v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo Goal, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Arthur v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh Arthur nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Andre Gomes s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/2-doi-bong-thanh-london-dai-chien-vi-sao-barca-172-184107.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</span>, M.U c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. 35 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Barca b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Valencia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Clement Lenglet c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio, Barca c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet c\u1ee7a Sevilla v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lenglet\" title=\"Lenglet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/barca-cong-bo-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-tuan-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lenglet c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sevilla, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn Barca th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Barca s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Lenglet, Sevilla s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Lenglet s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Umtiti v\u00e0 Pique cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean Barca c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Frenkie De Jong c\u1ee7a Ajax v\u00e0 Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3963","checkdouble":"190296"},{"date":"22:32 03/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nguoi-hung-dan-mach-bi-che-khong-bang-tham-hoa-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Steve McManaman g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-dan-mach-421-190118.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018</span> nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Con trai huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man Utd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c khi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 ba qu\u1ea3 penalty trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Luka Modric trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 hai.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i McManaman ng\u0103n Liverpool mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Schmeichel h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i McManaman ng\u0103n Liverpool mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Schmeichel h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/222642-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Schmeichel \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Schmeichel v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015-16 th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng Leicester City \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. N\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1edf r\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Steve McManaman g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Liverpool c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, n\u01a1i v\u1ed1n lu\u00f4n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ee9c nh\u1ed1i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Real Madrid tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Schmeichel: \u201cLeicester, v\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Schmeichel c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i g\u00ec h\u01a1n Loris Karius hay Simon Mignolet c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ai th\u00ec c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Schmeichel, Karius \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda ra sao trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid. K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111ang r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n r\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 Anfield, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, Donnarumma c\u1ee7a Milan hay Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke City.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-croatia-vs-dan-mach-vong-18-world-cup-2018-421-190137.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/du-am-croatia-vs-dan-mach.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-croatia-vs-dan-mach-vong-18-world-cup-2018-421-190137.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Croatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch: Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</span><br>\r\nCroatia vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 Zlatko Dalic v\u00e0 Age Hareide ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3962","checkdouble":"190308"},{"date":"00:39 04/07","title":"H\u00e0ng hot tuy\u1ec3n Nga ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u1ee5 huynh nh\u00e0 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111ang thi nhau \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League khi sau cha th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb9 anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a con trai.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/gau-nga-vao-tu-ket-co-nhung-gia-tri-lon-hon-ca-chien-thang-421-190169.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 G\u1ea5u Nga \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018</span> t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang may r\u1ee7i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">X\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng m\u1edbi, t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Igor Akinfeev \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Artem Dzyuba hay si\u00eau d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Denis Cheryshev, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qu\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Aleksandr Golovin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Golovin tuy\u1ec3n Nga sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Golovin tuy\u1ec3n Nga sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mua Golovin trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec3n trai tu\u1ed5i 22 l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m nay khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Arsenal, c\u00f2n gi\u1edd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m th\u00e0nh London Chelsea. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Golovin th\u00ec c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d c\u1ee7a\u2026 ph\u1ee5 huynh nh\u00e0 anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCon trai t\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Sasha \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh r\u1ed3i, n\u00f3 t\u1ecf r\u1ea5t h\u0103ng say r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d \u2013 \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Golovin cha v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ee3 \u00f4ng Svetlana ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, CSKA Moscow \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 con trai t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 chi ti\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec ch\u01b0a ai bi\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Sacha l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n cho World Cup. Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfp sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n minh ch\u1ee9ng cho d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf Premier League c\u1ee7a Golovin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng Arsenal hay Chelsea c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u1ec1 tay Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus-176-188909.html\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tien-gan-toi-golovin-172-189928.html\">Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi sao s\u00e1ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\">NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3961","checkdouble":"190313"},{"date":"01:40 04/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Uruguay x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/gettyimages-988121142.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cha c\u1ee7a Lucas Torreira ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/uruguay-21-bdn-ngay-ronaldo-phai-ghen-ti-voi-song-sat-suarez-cavani-421-190051.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span> m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ghi danh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. Trong khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Edinson Cavani t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng, Lucas Torreira \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Cristiano Ronaldo b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/gettyimages-988121142.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mua Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1eaft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1ng v\u1eeba d\u00f9 chi\u1ec1u cao ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed5i 1m7. Kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean g\u00ec khi Torreira tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n cha c\u1ee7a Torreira \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 con trai khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 c\u00e0ng th\u00eam l\u00fd do kh\u1ea5p kh\u1edfi m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho con trai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngay sau k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y th\u00f4i, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd bay \u0111\u1ebfn London \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd tr\u1ea3 cho CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Sampdoria c\u1ee7a Lucas Torreira kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, sau h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Stephan Lichtsteiner, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-vui-dap-nga-man-trinh-dien-an-tuong-cua-nhung-hang-hot-421-189571.html\">Uruguay v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Nga: M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\">Neville khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-172-190091.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3960","checkdouble":"190314"},{"date":"00:08 04/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: MU chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/8/13/mu-troi-chan-thanh-cong-them-mot-sao-tre.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sam Johnstone c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn West Brom v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 6.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>Johnstone r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Aston Villa. Anh gi\u00fap The Villains ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng play-off th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJohnstone \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh 7 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Man United nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u01a1i ph\u00fat n\u00e0o cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Yeovil, Doncaster v\u00e0 Preston \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 3, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/west-ham-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-thu-mon-cua-mu-172-183201.html\" target=\"_blank\"> West Ham mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Johnstone</span>. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, West Brom l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 6.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Johnstone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft West Brom\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C MU chia tay Johnstone h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C MU chia tay Johnstone h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/CHINH-THUC-MU-chia-tay-Johnstone-he-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU chia tay Johnstone h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Johnstone \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 45 l\u1ea7n cho Aston Villa m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho West Brom m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 CLB v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp West Brom. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng Preston th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 lu\u00f4n k\u1ebft th\u00fac b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Man United ho\u1eb7c \u0111i t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i West Brom\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Darren Moore ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Johnstone</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft West Brom kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, HLV Darren Moore \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n The Hawthorns. V\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Johnstone trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJohnstone l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t vui khi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho West Brom v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-chelsea-len-80-trieu-euro-180-190275.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-190284.html\">Ajax ch\u1ec9 mua l\u1ea1i Daley Blind v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3959","checkdouble":"190315"},{"date":"00:52 04/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh ai-c\u0169ng-kh\u00f4ng-bi\u1ebft-l\u00e0-ai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong th\u1eddi gian World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 Manchester United v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. R\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 35 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5p \u1ee7 t\u1eeb t\u1ea5m b\u00e9 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ao \u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB gi\u00e0u truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant, t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba sau qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Fred v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot, ngay sau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chia-tay-johnstone-172-190315.html\" target=\"_blank\">chia tay \u201cc\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn\u201d Sam Johnstones</span> c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 35 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n th\u1ee9 ba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero trong khung g\u1ed7 Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190176.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190176.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3</span><br>\r\nTheo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3958","checkdouble":"190317"},{"date":"13:56 03/07","title":"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal c\u1eb7p k\u00e8 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a h\u00f4n v\u1edbi Chicharito","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hau-ve-carvajal-cap-ke-phong-vien-tung-hua-hon-voi-chicharito.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m gi\u1eefa tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 b\u00f2 t\u00f3t Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Lucia Villalon.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Chicharito xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f4 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal. Lucia Villalon mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb c\u00f9ng Carvajal c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pilar Rubio, Sara Salamo v\u00e0 Beatriz Espejel (n\u1eeda kia c\u1ee7a Sergio Ramos, Isco Alarcon v\u00e0 Koke) c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a h\u00f4n v\u1edbi Chicharito h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Carvajal t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a h\u00f4n v\u1edbi Chicharito h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/cc2-1635-1530586577.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lucia Villalon v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecnh m\u1edbi Carvajal. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Lucia Villalo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico Javier Hernandez Chicharito. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Daniel Carvajal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid\", t\u1edd AS b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Nga 2018, Lucia Villalon l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i World Cup cho hai \u0111\u00e0i Univision v\u00e0 Televisa Deportes. Tuy v\u1eady, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sau khi tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3c l\u00f3c cho m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i gi\u1eadn d\u1eef, b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 sau k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t hay x\u1ea5u, v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n\", Lucia Villalon c\u00f2n tag th\u00eam d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef \"T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 anh\" c\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLucia Villalon v\u00e0 Carvajal t\u1eeb l\u00e2u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3957","checkdouble":"190272"},{"date":"14:09 03/07","title":"Nam ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean m\u1eb7c v\u00e1y \u0111i l\u00e0m sau khi Nga v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nam-phong-vien-mac-vay-di-lam-sau-khi-nga-vao-tu-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3956","checkdouble":"190273"},{"date":"14:36 03/07","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t fan cu\u1ed3ng Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/them-mot-fan-cuong-messi-tu-tu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t C\u0110V \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn thua 3-4 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn Argentina thua Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 t\u00ean Monotosh Halder, \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Malda (t\u00e2y Bengal), \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMonotosh Halder \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan cu\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Leo Messi. Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng Argentina v\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Leo Messi thua Ph\u00e1p qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup, Monotosh Halder \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 b\u1ecf \u0103n t\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111i ng\u1ee7 ngay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/NINTCHDBPICT000415355840-e1530544891798.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dinu Alex, C\u0110V \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn Argentina thua Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e1ng h\u00f4m sau, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 g\u1ecdi d\u1eady, Monotosh Halder \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng g\u00ec. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Monotosh Halder, cha m\u1eb9 C\u0110V \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eaft th\u1edf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCon t\u00f4i l\u00e0 C\u0110V Argentina. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb \u1ed1m. N\u00f3 d\u00e1n m\u1eaft v\u00e0o TV k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi World Cup kh\u1edfi tranh. Ch\u00e1u n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 qu\u1eabn tr\u00ed khi Argentina thua nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y\u201d, \u00f4ng Mongol Halder, cha \u0111\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Monotosh Halder cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Malda th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u tra v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Argentina\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Dinu Alex, 30 tu\u1ed5i, fan cu\u1ed3ng Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi bang Kerala (ph\u00eda nam \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9) c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y s\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3955","checkdouble":"190276"},{"date":"15:35 03/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 5-0 U19 Philippines (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-philippines-15h30-ngay-37.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh U19 Th\u00e1i Lan 0-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu do d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U19 Philippines.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-299-190079.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-299-190079.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng BXH - LT\u0110 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLink xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp (Fanpage Onsport): <span href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Onsportchannel/videos/588930214837934/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.facebook.com/Onsportchannel/videos/588930214837934/</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- HLV\u00a0Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ebf 8 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, Thi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n Nam l\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/doi-hinh-xuat-phat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1eadm. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 12: Minh B\u00ecnh v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc b\u00f3ng \u0111i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 20: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m sao ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp trung b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 22: U19 Philippines \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi Ph\u1ea1m\u00a0V\u0103n Nam ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt may, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00ca\u0111\u00ea Y E Li Ni \u00ca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 26:\u00a0Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Minh B\u00ecnh t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa b\u00ean trong kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 30: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U19 Philippines.\u00a0R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a \u01b0u th\u1ebf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi L\u00ea V\u0103n Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB\u00a0H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay, v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 39: D\u00f9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n U19 Philippines v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c song ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 42:\u00a0QU\u00c1 \u0110\u00c1NG TI\u1ebeC. Minh B\u00ecnh c\u0103ng ngang qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t L\u00ea V\u0103n Nam v\u00e0o t\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly c\u00f3 v\u00e0i m\u00e9t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft th\u00fac ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0T\u1ea5n Ho\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 50: U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 2-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho L\u00ea V\u0103n Nam ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 55:\u00a0U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 3-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. S\u1ed1 18 Minh\u00a0B\u00ecnh, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o\u00a0HAGL, l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-0 v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 65: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 h\u00f2ng mang ra d\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh l\u00fac c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 73: U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 4-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 4 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 82: U19 Philippines su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat xa uy l\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 86:\u00a0U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 5-0 U19 PHILIPPINES. Trung v\u1ec7 Duy Ki\u00ean c\u1ee7a HAGL\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n sau qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i theo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV\u00a0Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n\u00a0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Philippines 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 37 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Philippines 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 37 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Truc-tiep-U19-Viet-Nam-vs-U19-Philippines-15h30-chieu-hom-nay-37-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3954","checkdouble":"190270"}]}